_sText:
Okay. Here is the Beta version of FY_Dust
(http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/148356)
After working on this a while after reading PaiN_Agents great feedback, here's the result.
Aprox 1 week to do this Beta version.
Alot of credit to Valve.
Their 3D skybox, and De_dust Hall used, their soundscape.
This map has many many more features then the previouse version of FY_Dust.
-More props.
-More detail.
-Fixed tower/Beta.
-Fixed props.
-Lots of spawns, 40+
-Features as listed above & below.
-Still AI noded, works great with bots.
-More decals.
-Fixed CT's beeing able to spawnkill T's easily, multiple exits & spawns.
-Beta walls/fences.
-More lighting affects, wind & others..
-Wider, larger map. 
-More spawns for T & CT.
-Soundscapes. (Valves).
- Lots, lots more.
